Class GtfsBaseReader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.gtfs.readers.GtfsBaseReader<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GtfsAgencyReader, GtfsCalendarDatesReader, GtfsCalendarReader, GtfsFareAttributesReader, GtfsFareRulesReader, GtfsFeedInfosReader, GtfsFrequenciesReader, GtfsRoutesReader, GtfsRoutesSupplementReader, GtfsShapesReader, GtfsStopsReader, GtfsStopsSupplementReader, GtfsStopTimesReader, GtfsTransfersReader, GtfsTripsReader

    public abstract class GtfsBaseReader<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    For parsing a GTFS file. Does all of the hard work. This class is abstract because it needs to be subclassed to read in specific GTFS file type.

    SkiBu Smith
